{
  "stem": "26699.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES] While [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Inaki ?] was trying to break through the door, and we were hiding ourselves under the bed, I was six years old.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother begged me, asked me not to speak and not to cough.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In this way, she saved my life for the first time in that day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But after [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Inaki ?] left with his loot, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Germans started to climb the staircase of the first floor to round up the Jews as they did in Poland or in other parts of Europe.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They weren't petty criminals like [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Inaki. ?] They were professionals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when they penetrated into our flat, the first place they went, went to the bedroom to the bed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They turned the bed up, and the three of us were facing a couple of German heroes, fully armed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I can't explain until now why they didn't shoot us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were on the floor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They could have done.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one of these glorious soldiers asked us to get up, go through the door, and to follow his instructions.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES] My father was in the front, I was in the middle, my mother in the back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this I still can remember, blond, young, powerful, pushed my mother with the butt of his rifle down the staircase.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES] She rolled down a full flight of the stairs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She broke the knee.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for the rest of her life, she suffered from this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then he directed us to the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the three of us, with the hero in the back with his rifle, with hands up, we were herded to the concentration place.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was quite a long walk, I would say about half an hour.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
